SystemRequirements: OpenMP
Description: Random Hazard Forests (RHF) extend Random Survival Forests (RSF) by directly estimating the hazard function and supporting time-dependent covariates. This enables flexible modeling of dynamic survival data using an ensemble of decision trees trained under a nonparametric hazard-based loss function.
